    <item>
      <title>加纳执政党面临债务危机后选举失败的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/ghana-election-ex-president-mahama-leads-in-opinion-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳政府已监督了大部分公共债务的重组，获得了 30 亿美元的国际货币基金组织救助，并重启了这个西非国家的经济。但这可能不足以让执政党及其总统候选人在周六的选举中免于失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/ghana-election-ex-president-mahama-leads-in-opinion-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界首富现在是美国最大的政治捐助者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/the-world-s-richest-man-is-now-america-s-biggest-political-donor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年，埃隆·马斯克向政治团体投入了至少 2.74 亿美元，这股消费狂潮帮助唐纳德·特朗普赢得了总统大选，并为自己赢得了一个新头衔：选举周期中捐赠最多的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/the-world-s-richest-man-is-now-america-s-biggest-political-donor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 03:40:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平新一轮军事清洗是他驱逐敌对势力以来最大规模的清洗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/xi-s-biggest-military-purge-in-years-spotlights-frustration-with-armed-forces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席首次罢免数名高级将领，旨在铲除共产党内部的敌对势力。如今，他甚至还罢免了自己忠诚的一名将领，这表明军队出现了新的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/xi-s-biggest-military-purge-in-years-spotlights-frustration-with-armed-forces</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 03:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
