    <item>
      <title>印度高级外交官将访问孟加拉国以缓解紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/top-india-diplomat-likely-to-visit-bangladesh-to-defuse-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名孟加拉国官员表示，印度外交大臣将于下周访问达卡讨论双边关系，以期在就达卡政府突然更迭和对待宗教少数派问题进行数周激烈辩论之后修复两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/top-india-diplomat-likely-to-visit-bangladesh-to-defuse-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 12:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
